0.name: Chair, clear/chrome plated
0.description: A transparent chair that mirrors its surroundings. It picks up the colors of the room and appears to be floating. And because there’s flexibility in the seat, you may feel like you are floating too.

1.name: Junior chair, white
1.description: Too big for a high chair, but too short for a regular chair? Then a junior chair is perfect – high enough for the dining table, and with comfy support for the feet. Made for enjoyable dinners and crafting.

2.name: Folding chair, black
2.description: The chair is lightweight and easy to take out and unfold when you extend your table for extra dinner guests. Just as easy to fold and store when not in use.

3.name: Office chair, Vissle dark gray
3.description: This ergonomic office chair keeps you comfy and focused with features like a manually adjustable tilt tension, and head-/armrests to help relax the muscles in your neck and back. 10 year guarantee.

4.name: Loveseat 2 Seat Sofa
4.description: We launched KLIPPAN sofa in the 1980s and it’s still a favorite. It's comfortable, fits almost everywhere and has many covers to choose from. A modern and timeless classic!

5.name: Laptop stand, black-brown/glass
5.description: Metal and tempered glass give this laptop stand an open and airy feel. Place it next to the sofa and ta-da! You suddenly have a stylish and comfortable home office.

6.name: Children's table
6.description: At IKEA, we love to develop products that can be used together in a smart way. That’s why TROFAST storage boxes fit under the top of the table. Your child can keep toys at hand – and clean up in a jiff!

7.name: Extendable table, black
7.description: Everyone faces each other around a round table and you can make room for socializing by simply adding a leaf. A traditional look with details like the turned leg gives it that little extra.

8.name: 8-drawer dresser, white stain
8.description: A classic larger-sized chest of drawers in solid wood, with a traditional look and modern function. Quiet, smooth-running drawers make it easy to organize your things. Psst! Please attach to the wall.

9.name: Drawer unit on casters, white
9.description: A clean look that’s easy to like and mix with other styles, either supporting a desk or standing alone. The back is finished so you can place it in the middle of the room – all sides are just as beautiful.

10.name: 3-drawer chest, white stain
10.description: A classic chest of drawers in solid wood, with a traditional look and modern function. Quiet, smooth-running drawers makes it easy to organize your things. Psst! Please attach to the wall.

11.name: Wardrobe with 3 doors, white
11.description: Small spaces need smart storage. This wardrobe has a clothes rail for shirts and dresses, shelves for folded clothes, shoes and bags – and a mirror door too so you avoid needing to mount a separate mirror.

12.name: Shelf unit with 4 inserts, white
12.description: Place this KALLAX combination either standing or horizontally as a sideboard depending on your space. Handy drawers and inserts hide things that tend to get cluttered and are nicely finished on both sides.

13.name: Desk, ash veneer
13.description: We’re proud of our LISABO series, awarded with the prestigious, international Red Dot Award, for its design. The products are durable, sturdy and easy to assemble, yet look light and hand-crafted.

14.name: Corner desk-right, white/black
14.description: This sturdy desk is built to outlast years of coffee and hard work. You get a generous work surface and a clever solution to keep cords in place underneath.

15.name: Desk, black-brown
15.description: A clean look that’s easy to like, coupled with a clever design that keeps messy cables out of sight. The back is finished so you can place it in the middle of the room – all sides are just as beautiful.
